{"tid":2148264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[違反國安法]抖陰香港搞金融","createTime":"2020-08-09T23:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T08:15:31.000Z","uid":245372,"like":28,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb79447d1175b6a5909c560c675584df55600cb","tid":2148264,"uid":245372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T23:08:31.000Z","msg":"優先請大陸人，即係覺得香港人唔係中國人，違反國安法加種種歧視，可唔可以舉報？<br />\n<br />\n抖音母企字節跳動（ByteDance）面臨各國封殺，旗下國際業務TikTok亦撤出香港市場。不過《蘋果》發現，該公司籌謀進軍本港金融業，正就「松鼠証券」申請商標註冊，涉及證監會的第1、4、5、6及9類業務，近月積極招兵買馬，並優先聘請「港漂」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200810/FNMVFH7N7REFNLWOM64OOMUYQM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200810%2FFNMVFH7N7REFNLWOM64OOMUYQM%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YgHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=fcaaa7e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200810%2FFNMVFH7N7REFNLWOM64OOMUYQM%2F&h=9d482dc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200810/FNMVFH7N7REFNLWOM64OOMUYQM/</a>"},{"pid":"5e82b5e115b4971716769a5c7c79d8e183f840b9","tid":2148264,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T23:09:18.000Z","msg":"開始搵救生艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1bbf61a476df394b54f3e2eb577acc412582cc","tid":2148264,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T23:10:46.000Z","msg":"留名睇畀美國搞多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d51a02f52ded907b3808a8a5350dcec5727982d","tid":2148264,"uid":199957,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T23:11:39.000Z","msg":"又係殖民地企業 優先請本國人 唔請原住民"},{"pid":"bc08ede5581d1ef390c24fada968b267a21a9223","tid":2148264,"uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"1d51a02f52ded907b3808a8a5350dcec5727982d","tid":2148264,"uid":199957,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":